STEPMOTHER AND BUSINESS PARTNER GUILTY OF MURDER PLOT<
By Jane Merrick, PA News<
Business partners Sylvia Paterson and John Holmes were today found guilty of
conspiring to murder her stepson and his wife.<
Paterson, 55, and Holmes, 43, had denied conspiring to murder Paul and Sarah
Paterson.<
But the jury returned a guilty verdict after three days of deliberations at
Manchester Crown Court.<
